Download live wallpaper and install. (if download from Google, automatically installed)2. Long press home screen3. Select Wallpaper and then select Live Wallpaper4. Select " Harry Styles Live Wallpaper "5 Press Set As WallpaperHarry Styles is part of ONE DIRECTION. One Direction are a British-Irish boy band formed in London in 2010, consisting of members Niall Horan, Zayn Malik, Liam Payne, Harry Styles and Louis Tomlinson. They signed to Simon Cowell's record label Syco Records after being formed and placing third in the seventh series of British television music competition The X Factor. They later signed in North America to Columbia RecordsOne Direction have been described as sparking a resurgence in the boy band concept, and of forming part of a new "British Invasion" in the United States. As of June 2012, according to Nick Gatfield, the chairman and chief executive of Sony Music Entertainment UK, One Direction represent a $50 million business empire. Their work has earned them awards and nominations. One Direction have supported various charities and foundations, and have commercial endorsements with PokÃ©mon, Nokia, HarperCollins and Hasbro.
